Et si nous lui écrivions
un petit mot amical ?

49
00:03:07,846 --> 00:03:09,515
"Cher

50
00:03:09,598 --> 00:03:11,225
abruti

51
00:03:11,308 --> 00:03:13,060
incompétent. "

52
00:03:14,937 --> 00:03:19,358
